		<label>Stormhawk</label>
		<description>The Stormhawk Flayer is a versatile Space Marine flyer designed for close air support. Armed with potent flamer-based weapons, it can rain fire onto enemy infantry and light fortifications, clearing paths for ground forces while maintaining high speed and maneuverability to evade counterattacks. \n\n&lt;color=#bb8f04&gt;Crew:&lt;/color&gt; Driver x1\n&lt;color=#bb8f04&gt;Fuel type:&lt;/color&gt; Chemfuel</description>
		
